PrecisSetting aside of the election of RONALD CRAIG GEORGE who was elected to the office of councillor by the CHIPPEWAS OF KETTLE AND STONY POINT BAND OF INDIANS in Ontario on June 16, 1992, due to a contravention of section 75 of the Indian Act.
